        AND_DO_HURRY_MASTER_LEST_YOU_RETURN_TO                                    = 7051,  -- And do hurry, Master! Lest you return to find your poor moogle friend lying prostrate in a pernicious puddle of rainwater, kupo...
        THANK_YOU_MASTER_BUT_OUR_LEAK_IS_IN                                       = 7052,  -- Thank you, Master, but our leak is in another Mog House! Bring this to me when we're back home in [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst], won't you, kupo?
        YOU_VE_FOUND_THEM_KUPO_I_KNEW_I                                           = 7053,  -- You've found them, kupo! I knew I could count on you. That's what I tell all my moogle buddies. Why, my master is the boldest, brightest, bestest master of them all! Now we just take these, and...
        KUPOOOOOO_THERE_YOU_HAVE_IT_BETTER_THAN_NEW                               = 7054,  -- Kupoooooo`there you have it! Better than new! Why, a bevy of wild buffalo could barge in here this second and it wouldn't budge an ilm, I say!
        WHICH_REMINDS_ME_I_WENT_AHEAD_AND_RELAYED                                 = 7055,  -- Which reminds me, I went ahead and relayed the requisite reports to my manager at the MHMU.
        BUT_WOULDN_T_YOU_KNOW_IT_KUPO_IT                                          = 7056,  -- But wouldn't you know it, kupo? It seems there's been a trifling bit of trouble at one of our Rent-a-Rooms in Jeuno as well!
        YOU_KNOW_THE_ONE_RIGHT_ACROSS_FROM_DURABLE                                = 7057,  -- You know the one, right across from Durable Shields. Whatever could have gone wrong, kupo?
        WELL_THERE_S_NOTHING_TO_BE_LEARNED_LOLLYGAGGING                           = 7058,  -- Well, there's nothing to be learned lollygagging around here. Come, Master, we're off to Jeuno!
        LITTLE_DID_ANYONE_SUSPECT_THAT_THIS_WOULD_PROVE                           = 7059,  -- Little did anyone suspect that this would prove to be only the beginning of a harrowing nightmare unheard of in the annals of mooglekind...
        DO_SOMETHING_READ_INSTRUCTIONS_CHANGE_PARAMETERS_TELEPORT_TO              = 7060,  -- Do something? Read instructions. Change parameters. Teleport to key locations. Warp to home point. Receive items. Obtain 100,000,000 gil. Do nothing.
        HAIL_ADVENTURER_I_AM_THE_MOST_MIGHTY_OF                                   = 7061,  -- Hail, adventurer! I am the most mighty of moogles, my miraculous magicks able to alter all manner of arcane attributes!
        BUT_BE_FOREWARNED_KUPO_ONCE_MODIFIED_BY_MOOGLE                            = 7062,  -- But be forewarned, kupo! Once modified by moogle magick, your parameters cannot be restored to their prior state!
        FURTHERMORE_YOU_MAY_TRADE_A_MOOGLE_STORAGE_SLIP                           = 7063,  -- Furthermore, you may trade a moogle storage slip to me to wipe it clean, or mystically entrust its entire contents to me. Quite convenient, wouldn't you say?
        ADJUST_PARAMETERS_EDIT_MAIN_JOB_LEVEL_RESET_ABILITY                       = 7064,  -- Adjust parameters? Edit main job level. Reset ability recast timer. Obtain merit points. Receive all spells/rolls/attachments. Unlock all jobs and support jobs. Cancel.
