        BUT_THAT_S_NOT_ALL_BESIDES_THE_MYTHRIL                                    = 7647,  -- But that's not all... Besides the mythril, there's some unknown magic source in it.
        IF_YOU_MENTION_MAGIC_THEN_YOU_THINK_OF                                    = 7648,  -- If you mention magic, then you think of Windurst, right? I was hoping to get the Rhinostery to check it out, so I came all the way here.
        BUT_NOW_THAT_I_VE_LOST_THE_ROCK                                           = 7649,  -- But now that I've lost the rock in question, I'm stumped. After all the dangers I went through to get my hands on that rock, too... Boy, am I at my wits' end!
