        ARRRE_YOU_GOING_TO_FIGHT_THE_GOOD_FIGHT                                   = 7661,  -- Arrre you going to fight the good fight along with us? That'd be grrreat...I think. Speak to Captain Rakoh Buuma and she'll set you right!
        HE_Y_YOU_SEEM_TO_BE_FROM_ANOTHER                                          = 7662,  -- He`y, you seem to be from another country...I think. If you'rrre looking for the Consulate of [San d'Oria/Bastok], then it's [in this area/west of here]...[across the Bomingo Round/in Port Windurst].
        WHAT_ARE_YOU_STARING_AT_HAVEN_T_YOU                                       = 7663,  -- What are you staring at? Haven't you ever seen a Mithra beforrre?
