        I_KNOW_IT_S_A_LITTLE_SUDDEN_WUDDEN                                        = 7705,  -- I know it's a little sudden-wudden, but they said they were in a fix because they couldn't find anyone to help them. So, erm, how about it then...?
        GOOD_CARRY_OUT_THAT_MISSION_THE_ORASTERY_IS                               = 7706,  -- Good. Carry out that mission! The Orastery is the ministry that rrruns a Mage Academy to improve the military's magic abilities.
        TO_GET_TO_THE_ORASTERY_YOU_HAVE_TO                                        = 7707,  -- To get to the Orastery, you have to go to the port area by heading back west from this gate. Your country is counting on you!
        I_ERM_I_HAVE_A_FRIEND_WHO_SERVES                                          = 7708,  -- I, erm, I have a friend who serves at the Orastery. H-he's so cool! Gee... I wish I could be m-more like him!
        O_ONLY_THE_E_ELITE_STUDENTS_FROM_THE                                      = 7709,  -- O-only the e-elite students from the School of Magic can go on to enter the Orastery. So, so the Tarutaru in the Orastery are the most brilliant magic users in the whole of Windurst!
        THE_HORUTOTO_RUINS_ARE_A_BUNCH_OF_OLD                                     = 7710,  -- The Horutoto Ruins are a bunch of old towerrrs out in Sarutabaruta.
        BUT_THEY_RE_ALL_FALLING_TO_PIECES_NOW                                     = 7711,  -- But they're all falling to pieces now... It was the Tarutaru who destrrroyed them. They insist it was all due to the Great Warrr, but that just sounds like halfling half-truths to me.
        YOU_RRRE_NOT_S_POSED_TO_GO_STRAIGHT                                       = 7712,  -- You'rrre not s'posed to go straight to them magical towers, y'know? You'rrre s'posed to go to the O`rastery first...I think.
        THE_ORASTERY_IS_IN_CHARGE_OF_THE_MAGE                                     = 7713,  -- The Orastery is in charge of the Mage Academy, y'know? That's where the Tarutaru practice their spells all day in order to perrrfect them. It's the big building in the port area...I think.
        THE_DETAILS_OF_THE_MISSION_WILL_BE_EXPLAINED                              = 7714,  -- The details of the mission will be explained when you meet with the Orastery's minister. I can't say he's the most pleasant of people, but at least he has guts.
        DO_US_PROUD                                                               = 7715,  -- Do us proud!
        GOOD_JOB_GLAD_TO_SEE_YOU_MADE_IT                                          = 7716,  -- Good job! Glad to see you made it back alive! I trust the mission wasn't too dangerous.
