        TEHEHE_I_KEEP_GOING_OUT_INTO_EAST_SARUTABARUTA                            = 8499,  -- Tehehe... I keep going out into East Sarutabaruta, hunt a whole lot of Mandragora, collect their four-leaf buds, then come back and sell them off here to make a killing-willing! I'm so richy-wichy now!t
