        HMM_THERE_S_GOTARU_BE_SOME_INTERESTING_STORIES                            = 8507,  -- Hmm...there's gotaru be some interesting stories floating around somewhere. Hey, you there, mister/missy]...have you heard any juicy tidbits of information lately?
