        HAVE_YOU_SEEN_THOSE_AUTOMATON_GUARRRDS_CALLED_CARDIANS                    = 8515,  -- Have you seen those automaton guarrrds called Cardians? They are made at the Manustery, herrre in Windurst Woods.
