        SET_WHICH_FLAGS_TE003OK_FLAG_JUST_BEFORE_TE003START                       = 8663,  -- SET WHICH FLAGS? TE003ok FLAG. JUST BEFORE TE003start FLAG. HANDED OVER ITEM. QUEST FINISHED.
