        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_WATCH_OVER_THE_CHOCOBO                                   = 10576,  -- What will you do? Watch over the chocobo. Tell a story. Scold the chocobo. Compete against others. Go on a walk (short). Go on a walk (regular). Go on a walk (long). ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- ---- Nothing.
        YES_NO                                                                    = 10577,  -- [Watch over the chocobo/Tell a story/Scold the chocobo/Compete against others/Go on a walk (short)/Go on a walk (regular)/Go on a walk (long)]? Yes. No.
        YOU_SHOULD_WAIT_UNTIL_YOUR_CHOCOBO_HAS_MORE                               = 10578,  -- You should wait until your chocobo has more energy before doing that...
        IF_YOU_WATCH_OVER_YOUR_CHOCOBO_IT_WILL                                    = 10579,  -- If you watch over your chocobo, it will gradually return your affection.
        TELLING_YOUR_CHOCOBO_A_STORY_WILL_HELP_IT                                 = 10580,  -- Telling your chocobo a story will help it develop a healthy psychological state. Remember that concentrating on your speech will have a slightly tiring effect on the animal, though.
        WHEN_YOUR_CHOCOBO_ACTS_STUBBORN_YOU_MUST_DISCIPLINE                       = 10581,  -- When your chocobo acts stubborn, you must discipline it. Remember that reproof is an act of love. It is important to scold your chocobo the moment it acts up!
        YOU_RE_INTERESTED_IN_ENTERING_YOUR_CHOCOBO_INTO                           = 10582,  -- You're interested in entering your chocobo into competitions? Strange...there were three others who mentioned the same thing. Well, it is good for their physical development, after all. I suppose it's alright as long as it's done peacefully.
        VENTURING_OUTSIDE_OF_TOWN_WITH_YOUR_CHOCOBO_WILL                          = 10583,  -- Venturing outside of town with your chocobo will improve the bond between the two of you. If you don't wander off too far, your chocobo should not get very tired, either.
        VENTURING_OUTSIDE_OF_TOWN_WITH_YOUR_CHOCOBO_WILL_2                        = 10584,  -- Venturing outside of town with your chocobo will improve the bond between the two of you. You should try wandering out just a bit sometimes. It might tire your chocobo a bit, but could have some positive effects as well.
        VENTURING_OUTSIDE_OF_TOWN_WITH_YOUR_CHOCOBO_WILL_3                        = 10585,  -- Venturing outside of town with your chocobo will improve the bond between the two of you. Wandering far from town on a walk will expose your chocobo to all sorts of new experiences!
        YOUR_CHOCOBO_ALREADY_HAS_A_NAME                                           = 10586,  -- Your chocobo already has a name.
