        I_WISH_I_HAD_MORE_TIME_TO_CHAT                                            = 13193,  -- I wish I had more time to chat, but an artisan's guild comes first and foremostaru, you see. Please excusey-wuse me, and do take care!
        IT_S_HERE_IT_S_HERE_THE_SEASON                                            = 13194,  -- It's here! It's here! The season of Celestial Nights is upon us! And to celebrate, the moogles are bringing together lost loves by offering free teleportation to San d'Oria, Bastok, and Windurst!
        IF_THERE_S_SOMEONE_YOU_VE_BEEN_LONGING                                    = 13195,  -- If there's someone you've been longing to see, just let me know and I'll warp you right to their side (provided they are in either San d'Oria, Bastok, or Windurst), kupo!
