        YOU_TOOK_ANOTHER_DIVE_INTO_THE_DREADED_DUNGEON_2                          = 13205,  -- You took another dive into the dreaded dungeon, kupo? Well, you deserve a little something for your preternatural perseverance, kupo.
        THIS_ISN_T_ENOUGH_TO_PROVE_YOU_REACHED_2                                  = 13206,  -- This isn't enough to prove you reached the goal as a dungeon-delving duo. You have to bring me the item your partner received to show that you were both successful, kupo!
        TO_GO_ON_THIS_FRIGHT_FILLED_FACE_OFF_2                                    = 13207,  -- To go on this fright-filled face-off with fear, you need a partner who can prove you reached the goal. Come back when you have a buddy in bravery, kupo!
