        CONGRATULATIONS_ON_YOUR_VICTORY_YOUR_NATION_HAS_BEEN                      = 13249,  -- Congratulations on your victory, [San d'Orian/Bastoker/Windurstian]! Your nation has been selected Crystal War MVN, kupo! As a reward, I shall teleport you to any nation of your choice!
